dump: L!This program cannot be run in DOS mode.

Paroxsym is a basic windows program that allows the user to send Ping packets. Unix machines allow users to specify the data to send in the ping packet, but windows doesn't support this option. Instead you can use the Paroxsym tool to send custom Ping Packets.
